{"word":"κατεφάλλομαι","slug":"κατεφάλλομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κατεφάλλομαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to spring down upon, rush upon</i>, <el>κατεπάλμενος</el> (aor2 <a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <a href='S:syncopated'>syncop.</a>) <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>for <el>κατ-έπαλτο</el>, <a href='S:vide'>v.</a> <el>καταπάλλω.</el><p/></div>"}]}